description:
The Rocks Pirates were a legendary and powerful pirate crew that sailed the seas until their defeat 38 years before the current storyline.
They were led by http://anidb.net/character/119385 [Rocks D. Xebec] and considered to be the most dangerous and strongest pirate crew of their time. They ruled the seas before the rise of http://anidb.net/character/697 [Gol D. Roger] and http://anidb.net/character/1959 [his crew].
name: Rocks Kaizokudan
